# AccreditationCenter — AI Context

> Rails 8.1.3 | Ruby 3.4.4
> Generated by rails-ai-context v5.10.0

## Stack
- Database: PostgreSQL — 11 tables
- Models: 11
- Routes: 116 across 18 controllers
- Async: 1 jobs
- Migrations: 30 total, 0 pending
- Auth: Devise + Pundit
- I18n: 2 locales (en, et)
- Assets: propshaft, importmap
- Performance: 20 issues detected

## Key models (11 total)
- **Answer** (1a, 3v) — belongs_to :question
  scopes: correct, incorrect, ordered
- **PracticalTask** (2a, 5v) — belongs_to :test, has_many :practical_task_results
  scopes: ordered, active
- **PracticalTaskResult** (2a, 2v) — belongs_to :test_attempt, belongs_to :practical_task
- **Question** (3a, 7v) — belongs_to :test_category, has_many :answers, has_many :question_responses
  scopes: ordered, active, mandatory, non_mandatory
- **QuestionResponse** (2a, 2v) — belongs_to :test_attempt, belongs_to :question
  scopes: answered
- **Registrar** (2a, 2v) — has_many :users, has_many :test_attempts
  scopes: with_non_admin_users
- **Test** (5a, 8v) — has_many :test_categories_tests, has_many :test_categories, has_many :test_attempts, has_many :questions, has_many :practical_tasks
  scopes: active, auto_assignable
- **TestAttempt** (6a, 4v) — belongs_to :user, belongs_to :test, has_many :question_responses, has_many :questions, has_many :practical_task_results, has_many :practical_tasks
  scopes: ordered, not_completed, completed, in_progress, recent, passed, failed
- **TestCategoriesTest** (2a, 3v) — belongs_to :test, belongs_to :test_category
- **TestCategory** (3a, 4v) — has_many :test_categories_tests, has_many :tests, has_many :questions
  scopes: active
- **User** (3a, 5v) — belongs_to :registrar, has_many :test_attempts, has_many :tests
  scopes: not_admin, admin

